On a day to day basis I work with CISO, CIO, SOC managers, SOC analyst, cyber risk specialist, incident responders to understand cyber security challenges and discuss strategies on how cyber security can be a business enabler.

i've worked as a SOC manager and led a large team of SOC analyst’s with a Fortune 200 financial services firm running 24/7 operations.
